question: Will Trump win and nominate RFK to a cabinet position?

content.text: This market will settle as YES if Trump wins the presidency and he nominates Robert F Kennedy to a cabinet position by January 31, 2025.
Update: An unofficial announcement will be sufficient for the market to resolve as YES. The nomination need not be received by the Senate by the resolution date.
